<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
Landing Page Demo Data Integration for GrowERP
This snippet can be added to the PartyServices100.xml demo data loading service
to automatically create landing page demo data when demo data is loaded.

Instructions:
1. Find the "load#demo" service in PartyServices100.xml (around line 3600)
2. Add this code block after the activities section and before the closing </while> tag
3. The landing page demo data will be created automatically when demo data is loaded

This creates:
- 1 Main business assessment landing page with all components
- 1 Tech startup landing page variation
- Complete sections, credibility info, statistics, and CTAs for each page
-->

